{"tid":328793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（EDC定律）同一件淘寶貨，大媽穿被批包糉，正妹穿讚「童貞殺」","createTime":"2017-07-20T00:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T02:32:32.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a36505a813c96a043d3a11df9795b8ae7685a5c","tid":328793,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:46:48.000Z","msg":"日本Coser宮本彩希日前穿上一套露胸、露背，又露肚臍的黑紗禮服，引起廣大討論。但有人卻發現，這套衣服就是之前網路上超紅的「淘寶童貞殺」，還貼出豐滿大媽穿上這件衣服的樣子，超大的差別也令網友無奈感嘆，「人正穿甚麼都好看，人醜穿甚麼都礙眼。」<br />\n<br />\n▼宮本彩希身材火辣。（圖／宮本彩希推特）<br />\n<br />\n▲淘寶「童貞殺」被大媽嫌醜　換正妹穿卻「瞬間變名牌！」。（圖／翻攝宮本彩希推特）<br />\n<br />\n宮本彩希穿的這套衣服2年前就在淘寶上紅過一次，當時就有人抱怨，自己看網站上的模特兒穿起來性感又高雅，所以才跟著買了，沒想到自己收到衣服以後，光是穿進去就有困難，好不容易穿好了，卻難看到不行，跟包肉粽差不多，「真的是同一件衣服嗎？我穿起來怎麼成這德行！」<br />\n<br />\n▼大媽的胸前其實也很有料。（圖／翻攝淘寶）<br />\n<br />\n▲淘寶「童貞殺」被大媽嫌醜　換正妹穿卻「瞬間變名牌！」。（圖／翻攝淘寶）<br />\n<br />\n判若兩件衣服的情況也引起網友關注，大家都對這種情形超級同情，「我可以理解，每次買網購都是這樣，別人穿是偶像明星，我穿是性騷擾猥褻。」、「陳冠希穿吊嗄出門被說好潮，我穿吊嗄出門被說好噁。」、「有些衣服就是吃身材啦，大家穿衣服還是要注意一點，把缺點隱藏，把優點秀出來！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/084642_98f5cfeb55efa168ec6bd466aebfa30c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F084642_98f5cfeb55efa168ec6bd466aebfa30c.jpg&h=222d2e27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/20/084644_9b72adb217cd03d9beb0660581115836.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F20%2F084644_9b72adb217cd03d9beb0660581115836.jpg&h=d3fdb244&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70788ed551e2454e1ad638475929269c21274c3f","tid":328793,"uid":53568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:49:38.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bcce15c49464f69b4b051860c17d34347ca4a4","tid":328793,"uid":996,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/25T67cX_d.jpg?maxwidth=640&amp;shape=thumb&amp;fidelity=high\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F25T67cX_d.jpg%3Fmaxwidth%3D640%26shape%3Dthumb%26fidelity%3Dhigh&h=396ac18b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e65d2150e68208e0fdcd1e7106246f99c2795dc5","tid":328793,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T00:55:26.000Z","msg":"有印象tvb一個中女演員都著過依件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9d8ddc2d8332e579575438a313eb2fa3c68bd0","tid":328793,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:24:20.000Z","msg":"Your face,your fate <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98374caa2c76d3e14616304526bf9749ae00ad0","tid":328793,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T01:45:10.000Z","msg":"呢件衫就算係女明星都唔係個個handle到啦"},{"pid":"dbfd5126c2585e0dc9cf9e8228f1ef8b76332f39","tid":328793,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T02:32:32.000Z","msg":"自曝其短怪得邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}